{"tid":1217794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭呢獲真係用心良苦 不服來辯！","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T14:21:13.000Z","uid":15933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3429ba262698efd1df9f70acfe10355e8fd4d956","tid":1217794,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"你地怪錯人啦！區區一個女人！賣身比香港<br />\n不惜一切都要推行  有咁急得咁急 12號 唔得 13號 再嚟！推到咁急 迫香港人不惜一切出嚟反抗  順便助攻埋台灣  比埋個人版台灣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等大家醒覺 令全世界睇清共X黨嘅醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次唔去盡 香港人就會比咗機會呢個邪惡軸心再度蠶食 一舖清袋 <br />\n<br />\n柒婆唔理同伙同佢割蓆 都一定要推！ 推到更多人知道強權就係橫蠻！暴力！冷血！香港、甚至全世界唔行出嚟唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攬炒 攬到同樓上大國一齊倒台為止！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港柒姐 萬歲！ 今獲真係多撚謝你呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FmcaVf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FmcaVf.png&h=ad727f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲廢老成日話示威者搞事！好地地咪唔會出嚟打鳩你班生蕃囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢老們 你地誤會啦！為咗林鄭咁強硬 想我地出嚟令到政府倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有一呼百應下<br />\n未來呢幾日見啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96a637fb6ee1928e70ef8769b76eca34266bc6d","tid":1217794,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142c495fb8fea50e124c9c6f0e7901ada8dd7629","tid":1217794,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c